==== Global Settings ====
Global settings can be changed by the instance owner (person who has spent the most time in the current instance without leaving), these settings can change a wide variety of gameplay mechanics, making the game harder or easier for both the human players and the GIGA.

Global settings consist of:

* Victory Points (The team that reaches this point total wins): 10-500
* Time Until Overtime Phase (The overtime phase begins after this amount of time passed): 10-500
* Level-Up Interval (during the overtime phase, Humans automatically level up at this interval): 2-30
* Initial Human Level (Sets the starting level for Humans at the beginning of the game): 1-10
* Human Movement Speed Modifier (Multiples the movement speed of the Human team by this value): 0.5-3.0
* Small Cannon Attack Power (Determines the attack power based on the total level of onboard Humans): 0.1-1.0

